      "Text": "Security update for zstd",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for zstd fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2021-24031: Added read permissions to files while being compressed or uncompressed (bsc#1183371).\n- CVE-2021-24032: Fixed a race condition which could have allowed an attacker to access world-readable destination file (bsc#1183370).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
